channel.title: Right now! < z7's 2006 Moparscape Annual Event! > TODAY!
channel.description:
[center][b][size=30pt]z7's Moparscape Annual Event![/size][/b]
is over!!!!! heres some pics!:
[URL=http://img247.imageshack.us/my.php?image=fdfghghfhxo4.png][IMG]http://img247.imageshack.us/img247/4395/fdfghghfhxo4.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img247.imageshack.us/my.php?image=gnmghnghnfj9.png][IMG]http://img247.imageshack.us/img247/7116/gnmghnghnfj9.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img247.imageshack.us/my.php?image=gtrhbyn6.png][IMG]http://img247.imageshack.us/img247/2373/gtrhbyn6.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img247.imageshack.us/my.php?image=hkhjghjnhgig1.png][IMG]http://img247.imageshack.us/img247/1470/hkhjghjnhgig1.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img247.imageshack.us/my.php?image=kjhkjhkhkod4.png][IMG]http://img247.imageshack.us/img247/9264/kjhkjhkhkod4.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img135.imageshack.us/my.php?image=ngfbfnfhnco4.png][IMG]http://img135.imageshack.us/img135/5201/ngfbfnfhnco4.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img247.imageshack.us/my.php?image=nmghnmfgaj8.png][IMG]http://img247.imageshack.us/img247/6733/nmghnmfgaj8.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img247.imageshack.us/my.php?image=sdhflfgjdfghs2.png][IMG]http://img247.imageshack.us/img247/3281/sdhflfgjdfghs2.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img247.imageshack.us/my.php?image=ykiljhmkm0.png][IMG]http://img247.imageshack.us/img247/8577/ykiljhmkm0.th.png[/img][/URL]
[s]whenever you see a "X" in the title, there was an update
[b]Updates to thread or event:[/b]
[ul][li][b]Autotalker now works just redownload it for it to work[/b][/li][/ul]
[ul][li][b]Autotalker guide added![/b][/li][/ul]
[ul][li][b]New time!!!!!!!!!!![/b][/li][/ul]
[ul][li][b]New world[/b][/li][/ul]
[b]Hello, I'm z7skillz7z7z. I've decided to host my own event for the Moparscape community. Details below.[/b][/center]
[ul][li][b]What:[/b][/li][/ul] We will all create level 3 accounts named "Moparscape01" to "Moparscape99" and spam up a free world with the autotalker attached to this message. I have a picture with the virus results just incase anyone wants the results and you dont belive in text.
[ul][li][b]When:[/b][/li][/ul] September 23rd, 2006 at 7:00PM EST (eastern standard time) If Any Community member or mod needs a reschedule, that can be arranged.
[ul][li][b]Where:[/b][/li][/ul] We meet behind Lumbridge Castle. World 7
[ul][li][b]Who:[/b][/li][/ul] Everyone who is reading this can come as long as they obey the rules and they use an account named "Moparscape01" to "Moparscape99".
[ul][li][b]Why: [/b][/li][/ul] Cause school started, which sucks, and I never hosted an event for you guys. Plus everyone will have fun. If alot of people show up the people with the lower numbers, like even if your number is "moparscape93" You will get a prize. actualy, almost everyone will get a prize!
[center][b][size=40pt]Rules[/size][/b][/center]
Not many, but MUST be obeyed!
[b]1.[/b] Listen to "Moparscape01" (me) and "Moparscape00" (if Moparisthebest comes, thats his account) at all times. [b]2.[/b] When spaming, use nothing hurtfull against other Moparscapers. [b]3.[/b] Uhh thats it, inless anyone thinks something should be added. [b]4.[/b] Forgot about this one, all charachters MUST be made like this: [IMG]http://img170.imageshack.us/img170/8984/accountlookhr6.png[/img]
[center][b][size=30pt]Spamming software[/size][/b][/center]
I have ran it thru Jotti and here are the results:
[IMG]http://img434.imageshack.us/img434/4421/hehehahabb4.png[/img]
The download is at the bottom of this page.
[center][b][size=30pt]How to get the autotalker to work[/size][/b][/center]
first, open it up and start the application. it should look like this:
[IMG]http://img316.imageshack.us/img316/199/at1si9.png[/img]
Click on that spot and it should look like this:
[IMG]http://img316.imageshack.us/img316/5060/at2sh3.png[/img]
Then after 5 seconds it should open, click "Add" at the Panel under the blue box. type in your message and choose effects:
[IMG]http://img316.imageshack.us/img316/6341/at3vh9.png[/img]
after that Click "Add" and the message will apear in the blue box, click on the message to highlight it and then log into rs and press F12.
ALAS the autotalker works!
[center][b][size=30pt]Anything else[/size][/b][/center]
As every event needs a crappy sig or picture, heres mine:
[URL=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,19639.0.html][IMG]http://img375.imageshack.us/img375/9598/omgwtfmj1.png[/img][/URL]
[code][URL=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,19639.0.html][IMG]http://img375.imageshack.us/img375/9598/omgwtfmj1.png[/IMG][/URL][/code]
If you can make a better one, your more than welcome to do that. :p [/s]
